To all those who are whining about it not working:
1) Create a new folder in C:\Program Files called "Singles Install Files"
2) Once the download is complete, copy all the files that were downloaded to the new folder you just created (C:\Program Files\Singles Install Files)
3) Click on the "setup.exe" icon. THIS IS IMPORTANT: CLICK ON SETUP.EXE DO NOT CLICK ANYTHING ELSE OR INSTALL WILL NOT WORK!
4) Start playing!
5) LEARN TO USE YOUR FUCKING COMPUTER!
